135
00:10:15,660 --> 00:10:16,900
Give me a hand.

136
00:10:21,020 --> 00:10:21,860
Okay.

137
00:10:23,660 --> 00:10:25,020
Let's plant flowers together.

138
00:10:28,900 --> 00:10:32,410
♪We won't part anymore♪

139
00:10:32,560 --> 00:10:38,120
♪We won't keep our distance♪

140
00:10:38,120 --> 00:10:41,880
♪I'll lie in your arms♪

141
00:10:41,890 --> 00:10:45,620
