150
00:11:28,020 --> 00:11:28,900
We're going out in a minute.

151
00:11:29,020 --> 00:11:30,140
Yes, Ms. Ruolan.

152
00:11:33,060 --> 00:11:33,940
Come in.

153
00:11:34,260 --> 00:11:35,380
Why are you standing there?

154
00:11:43,940 --> 00:11:44,780
Ms. Ruolan,

155
00:11:45,140 --> 00:11:46,140
your coat

156
00:11:46,420 --> 00:11:47,380
