157
00:11:47,620 --> 00:11:48,460
Thanks.

158
00:11:57,580 --> 00:11:58,420
Have a seat.

159
00:13:12,140 --> 00:13:13,900
Hao, what are you doing?

160
00:13:14,220 --> 00:13:15,180
Ms. Ruolan,

161
00:13:15,740 --> 00:13:17,060
