168
00:13:34,940 --> 00:13:35,780
No...

169
00:13:38,780 --> 00:13:39,620
No,

170
00:13:39,940 --> 00:13:40,860
Ms. Ruolan.

171
00:13:41,460 --> 00:13:42,860
